The paper deals with the topic of local codes in distributed storage systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The proposed method involves cooperative repair, which is a technique used in networked systems (cs.SI) and communication networks (cs.NI). The paper also involves theoretical analysis and simulation experiments, which could fall under the category of computational complexity (cs.CC).
